<item>
            <title>[LU-18488] correct the strange use of llapi_resync_comp::lrc_synced</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18488</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;llapi_resync_comp::lrc_synced is used against intuitive in the mirror resync code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;llapi_mirror_resync_many_params()&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
                        written = llapi_mirror_write(fd,                            
                                        comp_array[i].lrc_mirror_id,                
                                        buf + pos2 - pos,                           
                                        to_write2, pos2);                           
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (written &amp;lt; 0) {                                          
                                /**                                                 
                                 * &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; component is not written successfully,  
                                 * mark it using its lrc_synced, it is supposed                                                          
                                 * to be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; before getting here.                 
                                 *                                                  
                                 * And before &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; function returns, all            
                                 * elements of comp_array will reverse their    
                                 * lrc_synced flag to reflect their &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;            
                                 * meanings.                                        
                                 */                                                 
                                comp_array[i].lrc_synced = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;;    
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
